    {
      "id": "37",
      "name": "Propriétés",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Source",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tutoriel",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Une fois le défi commencé, le Narval stellavore apparaîtra fréquemment depuis une",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "fissure interdimensionnelle",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "et vous attaquera, puis il disparaîtra dans la même",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "fissure interdimensionnelle",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "après un certain temps.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/5e90aedb3a37ef3eca6b9af3c5dea186_8746340059498441710.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(138, 109, 72)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Hostilité",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "En combat, le Narval stellavore accumule de l’",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "hostilité",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". L",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "’",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "hostilité",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "augmente automatiquement au fil du temps, mais vous pouvez également la provoquer chez le Narval stellavore en l’attaquant.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/463f78b02012ba3af8a1df076a856434_2053413719259019289.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Evitez les attaques du Narval stellavore et trouvez le moment idéal pour l’attaquer et accumuler de l’hostilité.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/f742f112dee14b762f23f5a5006d3dd2_7569103246385723800.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Infliger des DGT au Narval stellavore et détruire les tourbillons qu’il crée peut attiser son",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "hostilité",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "italic"
                      ],
                      "text": "Les attaques pneuma ou ousia permettent de détruire rapidement les tourbillons.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/6ce89e5f7686fd30c2dd9dbeadc49978_4557990817944523507.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#8a6d48"
                      ],
                      "text": "Ombres sombres",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Une fois que l’hostilité atteint son maximum, le Narval stellavore vous avale et vous finissez dans son ventre, où vous affronterez les mystérieuses",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "ombres sombres",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/75389f521ab9aa45f1431220bfa4c41d_8400498982521985310.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Régulièrement, les ombres sombres libèrent les",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "attaques des ombres",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "qui peuvent causer d’importants DGT, alors soyez prudents !",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/923067eb94f54726ffcd4a06c4710c6a_1244383035386305436.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "italic"
                      ],
                      "text": "Les attaques pneuma ou ousia peuvent interrompre les attaques des ombres et infliger des DGT aux ombres sombres.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/c3b1584c491d697f3d869ac6c77e03dd_590736304265079283.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Vaincre les ombres sombres dans son ventre infligera alors d’importants DGT au Narval et le fera entrer dans un état affaibli vous permettant de vous échapper de son ventre. N’oubliez pas de saisir cette opportunité pour l’attaquer !",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/29/29705491/13663351ccdf6286116e4f6e21c3d351_8281728342035382565.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
